{"questionId":"d5718376-6a71-41d6-aa0f-411bb7f3bb75_10","correctAnswer":"7","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Set up","content":"Substitute $x = 6$ into $g(x) = \\dfrac{6x - 1}{5}$:<br/>$$g(6) = \\frac{6(6) - 1}{5} = \\frac{36 - 1}{5} = \\frac{35}{5}$$"},{"title":"Solve","content":"$$\\frac{35}{5} = 7$$"},{"title":"Answer","content":"<strong>7</strong> is correct."}]}